data.message:
Do you guys really think our school is biased on grounds of religion? Who else has experienced this? As long as I was there.. I remember doing tilak of teachers and welcoming them on teachers' day.. I was informed last year tha Diwali was celebrated during assembly.. and now there are reports like whatever are circulating.. do share this post and stand in support of our school and principal.. I don't know why people are defaming our school.. I can say honestly our school is secular.. All teachers respect all religious views and preach them without any hesitation.. guys please support the institution which has made you the person you exist now! Best way to express gratitude is to support our school and stand by it.

 Holy Trinity School.. The best school in World😇
